ards will be bestowed on individuals who show exceptional promise to become future leaders in their fields  Awardees will be recognized at a ceremony on February  th       A list of past recipients can be found at http   research uic edu funding opportunities faculty awards researcher year awards http   research uic edu funding opportunities faculty awards researcher year awards Note  The nomination must be submitted through the OVCR online portal OVCR online portal  n nEligibility Criteria n n nOpen to all faculty  i e  tenured  tenure track  research track  clinical track  including research assistant professors  with a full time appointment at UIC  with at least the last   years at UIC  Otherwise  the nomination should be made to the Distinguished Researcher Category  nDistinguished nominees will be evaluated on their full body of work  with emphasis placed on significant contributions made over the past   years  nNominees must have been at UIC for at least the past   consecutive years as of the nomination deadline date  nIn exceptional cases  two investigators can be co nominated and will each be evaluated for the appropriate award  Rising Star or Distinguished Researcher  based on career stage  n n Eligibility Criteria  n nDeadlines n n nApplication  Monday  November          by      pm nAwards announced  December      nAward Ceremony  February         n n Deadlines  n nNomination Process n n nNominations can be submitted by anyone from the UIC community who is knowledgeable about a successful UIC researcher scholar  Although self nominations are accepted  reviewers tend to view these as less compelling than those submitted by an enthusiastic colleague  n n Nomination Process Nominations can be submitted by anyone from the UIC community who is knowledgeable about a successful UIC researcher scholar  Although self nominations are accepted  reviewers tend to view these as less compelling than those submitted by an enthusiastic colleague  n nNomination Content n n nApplicants must provide the information below in the order as outlined  nCover Page form   This is an online fillable form  It is not downloadable  You should complete this last when you are ready to submit your application online  Note  nNominations will be reviewed by multidisciplinary panels so care should be taken to explain achievements in a way that can be appreciated by non specialists in the field  For example  such as the typical number of publications for the given career stage  the prestige of the journals sub field  etc sub field and career stage  nFor Distinguished awards  with a focus on one or two accomplishments and major breakthroughs achieved within the past three years  Nominators may also describe how these research accomplishments have contributed to the research excellence at UIC  nFor Rising Star awards  with a focus on potential to become a leader in his her field in the relatively near future  Nominators may also describe the potential impact on research excellence at UIC  nStatement should be   pages in length  single spaced     point font  with   inch margins  date of PhD or other terminal degree  nInclude the dates and type of appointment for all listed institutions  nList of completed  current and pending extramural research scholarly support with a   i e  principal investigator  co principal investigator   nPresentation of research scholarship in professional settings such as a conference speaker lecturer  please indicate keynote  plenary  or invited  or installation exhibit  nList of relevant publications  within the past    years   nList of outreach and engaged public scholarship  n t tNote  The resume CV may not exceed   pages  Writers should note their relationship to the nominee  reviewers tend to value external letters  especially for Distinguished Researcher nominees  single spaced     point font  with   inch margins  n nOPTIONAL   No more than   pages of other materials supporting the candidate s achievements  e g  press clippings  award announcements  or news items  n nSummary of nomination package n n nCover page n n nOnline fillable form  complete last  n n nNarrative statement n n n  pages  single spaced     point font  with   inch margins n n nNominee CV n n n  pages n n nLetter of support n n n  pages  single spaced     point font  with   inch margins n n nLetter of support n n n  pages  single spaced     point font  with   inch margins n n nOptional supporting materials n n nUp to   pages n n nAny components exceeding the prescribed page limits will be truncated before review  n n n Nomination Content Applicants must provide the information below in the order as outlined  t tNote  The resume CV may not exceed   pages  n nSubmission Instructions n n nYour nomination package must be submitted on line at http   research uic edu royapp  This file should be appended to the Cover Page form which is completed and submitted online  Please allow yourself time to download the forms as well as Adobe Acrobat Pro so you can successfully submit the nomination  The system will not accept applications after   p m  on Monday  November           You will receive a submission confirmation email which includes your cover page information Submission Instructions Your nomination package must be submitted on line at http   research uic edu royapp  This file should be appended to the Cover Page form which is completed and submitted online  Please allow yourself time to download the forms as well as Adobe Acrobat Pro so you can successfully submit the nomination  The system will not accept applications after   p m  on Monday  November           You will receive a submission confirmation email which includes your cover page information http   research uic edu royapp or has the potential to chart  significant advances to the field  i e  new innovation  discovery  or methodology i e  presented  cited  or invited to keynote or has the potential to contribute  to applications beyond research journals and acade